articles.author: Dustin Gardiner, Christine Mui
articles.title: Can Silicon Valley make a governor? Matt Mahan is betting yes - Politico
articles.description: For all the region’s financial and cultural heft, the bastion of Big Tech has been a cul-de-sac of political power in California.
articles.content: But the test for Mahan is not only whether he can consolidate support in Silicon Valley. The more pressing question is if that will be enough. For all its financial and cultural might, Silicon Valley… [+5623 chars]
